The paper describes a web-based platform for interactive analytics and visualization of network data. This platform is designed to facilitate scientific research and collaboration. The paper does not focus on any specific application area, but rather on the platform itself. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are those related to data management (cs.DB), social and information networks (cs.SI), data mining (cs.SD), information retrieval (cs.IR), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
